data.description: Cute brick 3 bedroom home on 2.5 acres... with fireplace... new roof... gutters and downspouts...and new siding on back... huge garage/workshop with new garage door and a loft for storage or a kids club house or play room ...new windows ... close drive to Rockford and Chicago if you are looking for a week end getaway cabin...  walking distance to the river where fishing is fabulous  ... chicken coop if you want to experiment with having a few chickens... the acreage is like a park ... serene and peaceful with plenty of trees... kitchen is gutted... so you can put in the kitchen you want to have with a clean slate ...
